  "body": "Create tests that will cover scenarios for Dapp permission tooltip. Tests should be covered in nightly. Probably not all scenarios should be included.\n\n1. ensure dapp permission tooltip is shown upon launch on Dapps tab\n2. ensure you can close the tooltip and it will appear again with next app launch\n3. ensure you can click radio buttons \n4. ensure that first option prompts the dapp to ask permissions (select first radio button and open simple dapp). Simple dapp should ask for wallet and profile permissions one by one. Check that if you accept the permission requests -> you can see this setting in Profile -> Dapp permissions -> simple dapp\n5. check that you can revoke access for dapps (profile - dapp permissions - revoke access) -> then simple dapp should ask for permissions again\n6. check that if user selects second option then simple dapp does not ask for permissions\n\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/28752642/57443663-3d704580-7257-11e9-9c22-2e8608ae2b39.png)",
